name: Monet'spaintings
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: monet paintings
des:
This skill presents 23 works by French painter Claude Monet, trying to follow a chronological framework.
The works covered are (non-exhaustive list):
- his first painting
- Impression, sunrise
- poppies
- woman with a parasol
- Rouen cathedral
- the nympheas (aka water lillies)
Information such as the date, the current location of the work are given.
 
The canvas presented appears on your screen if your device has a screen.
You will be able to request to repeat the comment, switch to the next canvas, or exit at any time.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
